    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">6</span>
     <span class="td">1</span>
     <span class="td">0</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
     <span class="td">-8</span>
     <span class="td">5</span>
     <span class="td">3</span>
     <span class="td">
     </span>
    </span>
   </span>
  </span>
  - the lower triangular matrix L
 </p>
 <p>
