  - extracts the singular values
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <b>
    <var>Σ</var>
   </b>
   =
   <b>vec2diag</b>
   (
   <var>
    <span class="vec">⃗</span>
    σ
   </var>
   )  =
   <span class="matrix">
    <span class="tr">
     <span class="td">
     </span>
